\c 19
\p
\s Shungu pamusoro pamachinda aIsiraeri
\p
\v 1 Zvino iwe, imba mariro pamusoro pamachinda aIsiraeri,
\v 2 uti, Mai vako vaiva aniko? Vaiva shumbakadzi, yaivata pakati peshumba, ichirera vana vayo pakati peshumba duku.
\v 3 Zvino yakarera mumwe mwana wayo, ikava shumba duku, ikadzidza kubata zvaingauraya, ikapedza vanhu.
\v 4 Marudzi avanhu akainzwawo ikabatwa muhuzha yavo, vakaiisa kunyika yeEgipita.
\v 5 Zvino yakati ichiona kuti yanyengerwa, kuti tariro yanyangarika, ikatorazve mumwe mwana wayo, ikaiita shumba duku.
\v 6 Iyo ikafamba-famba pakati peshumba; ikava shumba duku, ikadzidza kubata zvaingauraya, ikapedza vanhu.
\v 7 Ikaziva dzimba dzavo dzohushe, ikaparadza maguta avo; nyika nezvose zvayo ikava dongo, nokuda kokuwomba kwayo.
\v 8 Ipapo marudzi avanhu venyika dzakapoteredza akarwa nayo, vakakandira mumbure wavo pamusoro payo, ikabatwa muhuzha yavo.
\v 9 Vakaiisa muchirugu chine zvikokovonho, vakandoiisa kuna mambo weBhabhironi; vakaiisa munhare, kuti inzwi rayo rirege kuzonzwikwa pamakomo alsiraeri.
\v 10 Mai vako vakanga vakaita somuzambiringa, panguva yokuzorora kwako, wakanga wakasimwa pamvura;wakabereka zvakanaka, una matavi mazhinji, nokuda kwemvura zhinji.
\v 11 Ukava namatanda makobvu okuita tsvimbo dzavaibata hushe, musoro wawo ukakwirira kumusoro pakati pamatavi makobvu, ukaonekwa kumusoro-soro pamwechete namashizha awo mazhinji.
\v 12 Asi wakadzurwa nehasha, ukakandirwa pasi, mhepo inobva mabvazuva ikaomesa michero yawo, matanda awo makobvu akavuniwa, ndokuoma, moto ukaapedza.
\v 13 Zvino wasimwa murenje, munyika yakaoma ine nyota.
\v 14 Moto wabuda padanda ramatavi awo, ukapedza michero yawo, hapachine danda rine simba ringaita tsvimbo yokubata ushe. Awa ndiwo mariro, uye achazova mariro.
